      "id": "COR-001",
      "dimension": "COR",
      "severity": "medium",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "title": "JSON 文件锁超时后会删除仍可能被持有的锁",
      "location": {
        "file": "/Users/zhangsiqiang/Documents/person/other_code/QuickTab/src/main/services/storage.ts",
        "line": 80
      },
      "root_cause": "acquireLock 超时或遇到非 EEXIST 后无条件 rm(lockPath)，release 也无 owner token 校验；主进程和 native host 共享同一 index.json/commands.json。",
      "impact": "可能出现丢失更新、命令漏投或重复投递、索引覆盖和并发写入。影响共享存储层，范围大于单一调用点。",
      "fix_strategy": "锁文件写入唯一 owner token；仅确认 stale 后清理；release 只删除自己持有的锁；临时文件名加入 pid/token；增加跨进程并发测试。",
      "fix_complexity": "medium",
      "auto_fixable": false,
      "evidence": [
